import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Text,
  Center,
  VStack,
  Input,
  Flex,
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";

export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Flex
      width="100vw"
      height="100vh"
      bgColor="#121214"
      direction="column"
      justify="center"
      align="center"
    >
      <Text color="#FF577F">Kenzie Hub</Text>
      <VStack spacing="15px">
        <FormControl>
          <Box w="100%">
            <FormLabel color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs">
              Email
            </FormLabel>
          </Box>
          <Input placeholder="Digite seu email" bg="#343B41" />,
          <Box w="100%">
            <FormLabel color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs">
              Senha
            </FormLabel>
          </Box>
          <Input placeholder="Digite sua senha" bg="#343B41" />
        </FormControl>
      </VStack>
    </Flex>
  );
};
